1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:31,380 --> 00:01:36,080
[A Lonely Hero's Journey]

3
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:38,690
[Episode 36]

4
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:42,270
I can prove Gu Yizhong's innocence.

5
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:54,289
Witness, please testify.

6
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:54,920
Your name?

7
00:01:57,030 --> 00:01:58,030
Luo Wuqiang.

8
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:59,180
Your occupation?

9
00:01:59,670 --> 00:02:02,680
I'm the former Division Commander of the 6th Division of the New Fourth Army,

10
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,340
and currently a representative of the CPC Delegation

11
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:06,190
at the Nanjing Military Mediation Committee.

12
00:02:06,190 --> 00:02:07,650
I walk the righteous path.

13
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:09,930
Witness, please testify.

14
00:02:10,389 --> 00:02:11,270
Gu Yizhong

15
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:13,510
is officially a member of No. 90,

16
00:02:13,550 --> 00:02:16,010
but in fact, he's an informant for our Party.

17
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:18,270
My brothers and I have been targeted

18
00:02:18,670 --> 00:02:21,350
by No. 90 multiple times.

19
00:02:21,590 --> 00:02:22,550
It was Gu Yizhong

20
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:24,790
who saved us many times.

21
00:02:25,430 --> 00:02:26,910
Because of him,

22
00:02:27,170 --> 00:02:29,270
my 8,000 brothers and I

23
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,850
were able to formally join

24
00:02:31,510 --> 00:02:34,270
the Anti-Japanese National United Front.

25
00:02:34,510 --> 00:02:35,170
Your Honor.

26
00:02:36,810 --> 00:02:39,250
Luo Wuqiang's testimony can only prove

27
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,970
that Gu Yizhong once helped him

28
00:02:40,970 --> 00:02:42,240
and his 8,000 brothers

29
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:43,990
join the anti-Japanese cause.

30
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:46,280
It cannot prove that Gu Yizhong...

31
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:48,160
I have another piece of evidence.

32
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,970
Please review it, Your Honor.

33
00:02:49,990 --> 00:02:50,650
Present it.

34
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:58,420
This is an important report from our Party's

35
00:02:58,670 --> 00:02:59,780
underground member Huang Qiushou,

36
00:02:59,780 --> 00:03:02,390
given to our organization before his sacrifice.

37
00:03:02,390 --> 00:03:03,750
The report can prove

38
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:07,590
that Gu Yizhong is indeed an informant for our Party.

39
00:03:08,620 --> 00:03:09,710
He has been working

40
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:12,310
for the Anti-Japanese National United Front.

41
00:03:13,190 --> 00:03:13,960
Witness,

42
00:03:14,270 --> 00:03:16,750
is there anything else you need to say?

43
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,390
Yes.

44
00:03:18,450 --> 00:03:20,920
Gu Yizhong was framed.

45
00:03:20,950 --> 00:03:21,880
He's not guilty.

46
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:22,760
He's innocent.

47
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,910
He has always been working

48
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:26,040
for the Anti-Japanese National United Front.

49
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:28,460
I hope that this high court will immediately

50
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:31,780
declare Gu Yizhong not guilty and release him.

51
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,930
Witness, you may leave the stand and take a break.

52
00:03:41,530 --> 00:03:42,190
Your Honor,

53
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:44,910
Huang Qiushou has already sacrificed his life.

54
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:46,070
This report

55
00:03:46,090 --> 00:03:47,680
with unknown origins

56
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,840
cannot prove

57
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:49,870
Gu Yizhong's innocence at all.

58
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:50,550
Moreover,

59
00:03:50,790 --> 00:03:52,530
even if he were an undercover agent for the CPC,

60
00:03:52,530 --> 00:03:54,040
it could not cover up

61
00:03:54,180 --> 00:03:55,310
his heinous crimes.

62
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:57,730
Prosecution,

63
00:03:57,950 --> 00:03:59,750
do you have additional information?

64
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:00,350
Yes.

65
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,190
I have a document here

66
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:03,000
that can prove

67
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:06,040
Gu Yizhong personally planned the murder

68
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:09,630
of Ou Xinping, the Jiangsu District Director of the CBIS,

69
00:04:09,670 --> 00:04:11,220
and the intelligence agents of the CBIS.

70
00:04:11,220 --> 00:04:13,360
Is there any evidence or are there witnesses?

71
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:13,900
Yes.

72
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:15,630
Bring them in.

73
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:23,590
I'll kill you!

74
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,010
You deserve a horrible death!

75
00:04:25,010 --> 00:04:26,040
Traitor!

76
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,310
I won't let you go!

77
00:04:27,550 --> 00:04:28,820
-Silence!
-I won't let you go!

78
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:29,980
You won't get away.

79
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,070
Ou.

80
00:04:31,290 --> 00:04:32,960
If you really want to avenge your sister,

81
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,870
speak about what you know.

82
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,130
He's a traitor.

83
00:04:39,650 --> 00:04:40,730
A damn traitor!

84
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,810
He colluded with the Japanese!

85
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,950
Not only did he kill my sister,

86
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:48,570
but also more than ten agents of the CBIS.

87
00:04:48,710 --> 00:04:50,170
Even if you turned to ashes,

88
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:51,770
I would still recognize you.

89
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:53,770
Witness, state your name.

90
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,070
Your Honor,

91
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,200
my name is Ou Maochun.

92
00:04:57,909 --> 00:04:59,640
Ou Xinping was my older sister.

93
00:04:59,850 --> 00:05:01,980
We are Hakka from Meixian, Guangdong.

94
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:06,750
Here are all the identification documents

95
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:09,610
and certifications issued by the district office.

96
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:24,190
[Jiangsu High Court]

97
00:05:23,230 --> 00:05:24,110
Zhou Zhifei.

98
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,910
What exactly are you up to?

99
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,870
I am here as a prosecution witness

100
00:05:32,890 --> 00:05:34,280
to uphold justice.

101
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,700
Then why did you say

102
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:39,270
that Gu Yizhong killed the CBIS agents?

103
00:05:39,550 --> 00:05:41,409
Isn't that distorting the truth?

104
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:45,030
You should present this to the court,

105
00:05:45,310 --> 00:05:46,590
not to me.

106
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,030
Haimo,

107
00:05:51,790 --> 00:05:53,909
I feel for Gu Yizhong too.

108
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:55,670
I went to see him.

109
00:05:55,690 --> 00:05:57,510
I gave him a way out,

110
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:58,900
but he didn't take it.

111
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:01,280
Why did he have to choose this doomed path?

112
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:30,420
[Enhancing Prosperity and Happiness]

113
00:06:38,490 --> 00:06:40,680
We can't stay here anymore.

114
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:41,270
Come.

115
00:06:43,150 --> 00:06:44,140
Be good.

116
00:06:44,180 --> 00:06:46,710
We're going to Yancheng, to the countryside.

117
00:06:47,050 --> 00:06:48,950
Dad, there's someone there!

118
00:06:58,290 --> 00:07:00,620
[Third Prison]

119
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,870
Division Commander Luo said

120
00:07:00,870 --> 00:07:02,550
that if it weren't for the discipline of the organization,

121
00:07:02,550 --> 00:07:03,910
he would have already sent dozens of comrades

122
00:07:03,910 --> 00:07:05,190
to storm this stupid prison!

123
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:06,120
Absolutely not.

124
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,340
Haimo,

125
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,360
calm down first.

126
00:07:15,650 --> 00:07:17,910
If I escape now without clearing my name,

127
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,480
then I,

128
00:07:20,170 --> 00:07:21,870
my father, and Gu's Garden

129
00:07:22,470 --> 00:07:23,480
will forever bear the stigma

130
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,110
of being traitors to the nation.

131
00:07:25,110 --> 00:07:26,840
I will make sure they release me

132
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:28,030
the same way

133
00:07:28,030 --> 00:07:29,360
they brought me in here.

134
00:07:30,490 --> 00:07:32,820
I will walk out of the Kuomintang's prison

135
00:07:33,010 --> 00:07:34,110
as a patriot,

136
00:07:34,110 --> 00:07:35,310
with my name cleared.

137
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:45,190
The key to my case

138
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,540
is Ou Xinping

139
00:07:47,030 --> 00:07:49,230
and the murder of the those CBIS agents.

140
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,909
How did you know Ou Xinping?

141
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:55,340
She found me in Hong Kong at that time.

142
00:07:56,630 --> 00:07:58,420
We often talked about our families.

143
00:07:58,420 --> 00:08:00,550
She never mentioned having a brother.

144
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:05,590
I remember she once told me

145
00:08:06,290 --> 00:08:07,840
that her entire family was killed in an explosion.

146
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,790
Over 30 people,

147
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:10,480
and she was the only survivor.

148
00:08:11,590 --> 00:08:13,520
So why is there suddenly a brother?

149
00:08:14,610 --> 00:08:15,580
Is it possible

150
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,390
that he is an impostor?

151
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:18,280
It must be.

152
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:21,820
Can you ask the lawyer to investigate further?

153
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:23,030
Yizhong,

154
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,650
I know what to do now.

155
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:27,070
If we can prove he's an impostor,

156
00:08:27,590 --> 00:08:28,850
then all the witnesses

157
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:31,350
and evidence Zhou Zhifei used to frame you

158
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:32,900
can be overturned.

159
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,760
Haimo,

160
00:08:41,970 --> 00:08:42,700
thank you.

161
00:08:52,990 --> 00:08:54,650
It's snowing outside, right?

162
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,680
Be careful on your way back.

163
00:09:04,380 --> 00:09:09,770
Before Commander Luo...  Before Division Commander Luo left,

164
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:14,770
he told me that when Miss Xiao Ruotong sacrificed herself,

165
00:09:15,710 --> 00:09:17,630
he found a letter

166
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:19,230
in her belongings.

167
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,640
It's a letter from you back then.

168
00:10:01,220 --> 00:10:06,360
[Jiangsu Third Prison]

169
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:18,160
Dear Miss Xiao Ruotong,

170
00:10:19,130 --> 00:10:20,610
Before I met you,

171
00:10:21,070 --> 00:10:22,870
I never thought about marriage.

172
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:24,710
After I met you,

173
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:28,250
I never thought about marrying anyone else.

174
00:10:30,210 --> 00:10:32,330
I hereby formally propose to you.

175
00:10:33,190 --> 00:10:34,250
If you are willing,

176
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:37,520
it would be the greatest fortune of my life.

177
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:38,630
Gu Yizhong.

178
00:10:38,990 --> 00:10:40,110
October 8,

179
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:42,950
1941, Suzhou.

180
00:10:52,230 --> 00:10:52,830
Director.

181
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:55,520
Director Lin.

182
00:10:55,590 --> 00:10:56,450
How is it going?

183
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:59,690
He's an impostor. His surname is Ding.

184
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:01,590
I'm not Ou Maochun.

185
00:11:01,590 --> 00:11:03,320
And Ou Xinping is not my sister.

186
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:04,590
It was...

187
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:07,580
Zhou Zhifei who ordered me to do this!

188
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:09,430
Nonsense.

189
00:11:09,490 --> 00:11:10,840
Nonsense!

190
00:11:11,090 --> 00:11:12,940
You are the one talking nonsense.

191
00:11:12,940 --> 00:11:13,940
Zhou Youren.

192
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:16,940
Or should I call you Zhou Zhifei?

193
00:11:17,570 --> 00:11:18,240
Your Honor,

194
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,050
I have some

195
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:21,390
more compelling evidence here.

196
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,590
We have found some original materials

197
00:11:22,590 --> 00:11:23,660
from the No. 90

198
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:24,870
Suzhou Agent Station,

199
00:11:24,870 --> 00:11:25,850
which include documents

200
00:11:25,850 --> 00:11:27,750
signed personally by Zhou Zhifei.

201
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:28,360
Please have a look.

202
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,100
Present it.

203
00:11:31,830 --> 00:11:32,870
Zhou Youren,

204
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:36,830
you used to be called Zhou Zhifei, didn't you?

205
00:11:37,470 --> 00:11:38,800
I've had several names.

206
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:41,350
You were the Director at No. 90,

207
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:42,020
right?

208
00:11:42,710 --> 00:11:44,320
That was many years ago.

209
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:47,500
Is this report written by you?

210
00:11:47,710 --> 00:11:50,550
It contains a comprehensive and detailed account

211
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:51,830
of how Ou Xinping

212
00:11:51,850 --> 00:11:53,810
and other agents were betrayed.

213
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:55,350
I don't need to read it.

214
00:11:55,350 --> 00:11:56,210
It's a forgery.

215
00:11:57,590 --> 00:11:59,300
Not only does it have your signature,

216
00:11:59,300 --> 00:12:01,700
but the entire document was written by you.

217
00:12:02,470 --> 00:12:04,650
It couldn't be that someone forced you to write it, could it?

218
00:12:04,650 --> 00:12:06,180
The signature is a forgery.

219
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:06,900
Your Honor,

220
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:09,070
we request the next witness to be called.

221
00:12:09,070 --> 00:12:09,800
Call them in.

222
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:34,320
I didn't die.

223
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:41,980
Director Zhou,

224
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:43,950
it's me.

225
00:12:44,610 --> 00:12:46,380
I'm Zhang Jiping.

226
00:12:51,590 --> 00:12:52,390
Don't you recognize me?

227
00:12:52,390 --> 00:12:53,720
This is absurd!

228
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:54,910
Absurd!

229
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,000
Let me tell you,

230
00:12:58,850 --> 00:13:00,780
I am the chief commissioner

231
00:13:01,190 --> 00:13:04,720
of the Traitor-purging Committee of the National Government.

232
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:06,430
I was sent here by Mr. Dai

233
00:13:06,670 --> 00:13:08,950
to assist in eliminating traitors.

234
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:09,750
Jin Jichang!

235
00:13:10,030 --> 00:13:11,680
Make a quick decision

236
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:13,200
and eliminate the traitor!

237
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:13,930
Hurry up!

238
00:13:21,830 --> 00:13:23,990
We are going to eliminate the traitor.

239
00:13:25,050 --> 00:13:28,330
We aim to eliminate the real traitor, Zhou Zhifei.

240
00:13:33,470 --> 00:13:34,510
How dare you?

241
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:38,470
Take him down!

242
00:13:43,550 --> 00:13:45,290
I will report this to Nanjing.

243
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:47,180
I will have Mr. Dai

244
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:49,310
send troops here immediately!

245
00:13:49,990 --> 00:13:51,740
Nothing that happens in this court today

246
00:13:51,740 --> 00:13:53,030
will count!

247
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:54,070
Take him down!

248
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,280
How dare you!

249
00:13:55,710 --> 00:13:57,440
What are you doing? Let go of me!

250
00:13:58,630 --> 00:13:59,350
Let go!

251
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:00,950
Jin Jichang!

252
00:14:01,070 --> 00:14:02,790
How dare you!

253
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:03,710
Take him away!

254
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:06,380
Let go!

255
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,520
What are you doing?

256
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:09,920
I'm going to call Mr. Dai.

257
00:14:33,660 --> 00:14:38,170
[Jiangsu High Court]

258
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:49,990
What?

259
00:14:51,430 --> 00:14:52,960
You've been in there so long

260
00:14:54,230 --> 00:14:56,560
that you're not used to the outside world?

261
00:14:58,030 --> 00:14:58,830
I'm used to it.

262
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:02,710
I'm so used to it.

263
00:15:08,740 --> 00:15:11,210
You shouldn't come here often.

264
00:15:13,590 --> 00:15:14,470
Youfei

265
00:15:15,470 --> 00:15:17,330
came back from Japan two days ago.

266
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:19,310
I said I was bringing him to see you.

267
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,230
Why didn't you let him come?

268
00:15:23,630 --> 00:15:26,120
What's the point of coming to a place like this?

269
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,310
It's filthy.

270
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:29,470
Don't worry.

271
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:32,210
I'll be out in a couple of days.

272
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:36,470
Zhou.

273
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:40,550
It's okay. Just say it.

274
00:15:40,670 --> 00:15:41,630
He's one of us.

275
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:46,710
Is Mr. Dai not protecting you anymore?

276
00:15:49,390 --> 00:15:51,390
Nothing is final until the very end.

277
00:15:51,670 --> 00:15:52,630
Let me tell you,

278
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:59,750
Xu Enzeng is to blame.

279
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:04,860
Didn't he send me a letter a few years ago,

280
00:16:05,620 --> 00:16:07,280
hoping I'd return to the CBIS?

281
00:16:07,710 --> 00:16:08,950
I ignored him.

282
00:16:09,900 --> 00:16:11,830
Later, when I left No. 90,

283
00:16:12,190 --> 00:16:14,870
Xu Enzeng thought I'd definitely go back to the CBIS.

284
00:16:14,870 --> 00:16:15,990
But he didn't expect

285
00:16:15,990 --> 00:16:18,450
that I'd join forces with Mr. Dai of the NBIS.

286
00:16:19,070 --> 00:16:20,330
You don't understand.

287
00:16:20,350 --> 00:16:21,860
The CBIS and the NBIS

288
00:16:22,070 --> 00:16:23,850
have always been sworn enemies,

289
00:16:23,850 --> 00:16:25,790
like ice and fire—completely incompatible.

290
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:26,910
This Xu

291
00:16:27,110 --> 00:16:28,990
has really made an enemy out of me.

292
00:16:30,670 --> 00:16:33,070
It was Xu Enzeng

293
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:34,990
who went to Mr. Lifu

294
00:16:35,010 --> 00:16:35,930
and accused me,

295
00:16:36,050 --> 00:16:37,980
leading to what happened in court.

296
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:43,190
Xu Enzeng holds grudges like that?

297
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:44,190
Of course.

298
00:16:46,060 --> 00:16:47,350
Xu Enzeng claims to have

299
00:16:47,350 --> 00:16:50,110
a master's degree from CMU in the U.S.,

300
00:16:50,430 --> 00:16:51,110
but in fact,

301
00:16:51,110 --> 00:16:52,790
he's just a petty man.

302
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:55,390
Well,

303
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:57,610
wait outside for a minute.

304
00:17:02,190 --> 00:17:02,950
Zhou.

305
00:17:03,430 --> 00:17:05,230
I need you to find someone for me.

306
00:17:06,220 --> 00:17:07,609
Do you remember a man

307
00:17:07,910 --> 00:17:09,180
named Jiang Boxian?

308
00:17:09,589 --> 00:17:10,349
Yes.

309
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:12,540
His wife once gave me gold bars.

310
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:13,869
This Jiang Boxian

311
00:17:13,890 --> 00:17:15,849
is extremely capable.

312
00:17:16,470 --> 00:17:18,829
First, he's said

313
00:17:19,390 --> 00:17:21,430
to be a distant relative of Chiang.

314
00:17:21,670 --> 00:17:22,470
Second,

315
00:17:22,490 --> 00:17:24,810
he has very good relationships

316
00:17:24,839 --> 00:17:26,349
with both Xu Enzeng and Dai Li.

317
00:17:26,349 --> 00:17:28,510
Oh, right. He is now in Suzhou,

318
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:31,230
living in Crane Garden, which belonged to Mr. Li.

319
00:17:31,230 --> 00:17:33,550
He likes money.

320
00:17:34,270 --> 00:17:36,030
Give him a little something for me

321
00:17:36,030 --> 00:17:38,070
and ask him to apologize to Xu Enzeng

322
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:39,510
on my behalf.

323
00:17:39,630 --> 00:17:40,550
That way,

324
00:17:40,550 --> 00:17:43,000
Mr. Dai can easily go along with it

325
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:43,870
and get me released.

326
00:17:43,870 --> 00:17:44,950
Okay, Zhou.

327
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:47,630
I know what to do.

328
00:17:49,650 --> 00:17:50,430
Ji,

329
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:54,390
there's something

330
00:17:54,390 --> 00:17:56,720
I don't think I've ever said to you before.

331
00:17:59,500 --> 00:18:00,430
I love you.

332
00:18:06,670 --> 00:18:07,830
Go back.

333
00:18:11,490 --> 00:18:12,310
Zhou,

334
00:18:14,750 --> 00:18:16,350
I heard what you just said.

335
00:19:01,430 --> 00:19:02,350
Mr. Jiang.

336
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:12,910
Zhifei's request is not easy to handle.

337
00:19:15,670 --> 00:19:16,630
Mr. Jiang,

338
00:19:17,710 --> 00:19:19,110
our entire family

339
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:20,840
is relying on you.

340
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:29,430
All our possessions are here.

341
00:19:31,630 --> 00:19:32,830
I only ask you

342
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:36,030
to save Old Zhou's life.

343
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:36,710
Wait.

344
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:41,630
This thing you're wearing is our family heirloom.

345
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:43,510
It's from the palace.

346
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:45,860
Yes.

347
00:19:47,190 --> 00:19:48,070
Yes.

348
00:19:50,510 --> 00:19:53,630
It was a gift from Mrs. Jiang back then.

349
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:56,630
Ever since Zhou was imprisoned,

350
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:58,710
I've lost weight,

351
00:19:59,910 --> 00:20:01,590
and it no longer fits me.

352
00:20:06,230 --> 00:20:07,230
Please help me

353
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:09,950
thank Mrs. Jiang.

354
00:20:12,670 --> 00:20:15,150
Look at this hand.

355
00:20:19,350 --> 00:20:20,960
These little things...

356
00:20:23,910 --> 00:20:24,830
I hope

357
00:20:27,190 --> 00:20:29,190
Mrs. Jiang finds them to her liking.

358
00:20:36,950 --> 00:20:38,030
Please make sure

359
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:40,350
to put in a good word for Zhou

360
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:43,270
in front of Mr. Dai.

361
00:20:45,550 --> 00:20:46,670
Unfortunately,

362
00:20:48,150 --> 00:20:51,190
Dai Li's plane crashed into Daishan in Nanjing

363
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,110
the day before yesterday.

364
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:55,350
He's dead.

365
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:02,920
A crash?

366
00:21:06,910 --> 00:21:08,720
Mr. Yunong has passed away?

367
00:21:11,840 --> 00:21:13,790
It's in the newspapers today.

368
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:27,200
Yunong!

369
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:40,710
Zhou, do we have any other options?

370
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:58,760
[Keep quiet] [Keep quiet]

371
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:55,990
All rise.

372
00:21:59,070 --> 00:22:00,600
Zhou Zhifei, the criminal,

373
00:22:01,190 --> 00:22:03,340
conspired with an enemy nation

374
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:05,160
to rebel against his own country.

375
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,950
He is sentenced to death,

376
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:10,450
stripped of his civil rights for life,

377
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:11,880
and all his assets

378
00:22:12,310 --> 00:22:13,570
are to be confiscated.

379
00:22:51,390 --> 00:22:52,190
Keep up!

380
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:53,730
Hurry up!

381
00:22:54,870 --> 00:22:56,060
Don't dawdle!

382
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:58,370
Director Zhou asked me to see you off.

383
00:23:22,530 --> 00:23:27,940
[Jiangsu Third Prison]

384
00:23:28,430 --> 00:23:29,070
Zhou!

385
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:31,920
I'll go to Nanjing.

386
00:23:32,270 --> 00:23:34,790
I'll kneel at Mr. Chen Lifu's door.

387
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:37,810
We won't accept this verdict.

388
00:23:38,030 --> 00:23:39,350
We will appeal to the end.

389
00:23:39,350 --> 00:23:40,950
I've already hired a lawyer.

390
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,610
Didn't you say Director Ye...

391
00:23:42,610 --> 00:23:44,190
-Ji.
-You know him, right?

392
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:46,000
I'll go and see him...

393
00:23:46,070 --> 00:23:46,640
Ji.

394
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:48,550
Don't.

395
00:23:50,380 --> 00:23:52,110
Save me some face.

396
00:23:55,030 --> 00:23:56,000
Where's Youfei?

397
00:23:56,310 --> 00:23:57,910
Didn't I ask you to bring him?

398
00:24:02,510 --> 00:24:03,470
Is he here?

399
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:10,800
Alright.

400
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:13,590
I'll go get him.

401
00:24:23,230 --> 00:24:25,710
Go in there and see your father.

402
00:24:27,310 --> 00:24:28,510
See your father.

403
00:24:46,790 --> 00:24:47,740
Lift your head.

404
00:25:15,670 --> 00:25:17,820
You're almost as tall as Dad now.

405
00:25:21,610 --> 00:25:24,550
Youfei, let me see you.

406
00:25:41,970 --> 00:25:43,040
Young man!

407
00:25:56,610 --> 00:25:57,410
Son,

408
00:25:58,590 --> 00:26:00,450
Dad won't be around in the future.

409
00:26:02,260 --> 00:26:04,030
Take good care of yourself

410
00:26:05,830 --> 00:26:07,150
and your mom.

411
00:26:08,670 --> 00:26:10,190
Finish

412
00:26:11,230 --> 00:26:12,110
your studies.

413
00:26:13,430 --> 00:26:14,880
When you grow up,

414
00:26:16,790 --> 00:26:18,470
be an outstanding man.

415
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:31,230
Zhou! Zhou! Zhou!

416
00:26:31,350 --> 00:26:33,710
You have to leave our son with some final words.

417
00:26:33,710 --> 00:26:35,510
Leave some final words, please.

418
00:26:41,630 --> 00:26:42,470
Youfei,

419
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:45,680
listen carefully:

420
00:26:47,590 --> 00:26:51,430
Never, in this life, do anything to betray your country.

421
00:26:58,070 --> 00:26:59,070
Dad!

422
00:27:00,210 --> 00:27:01,380
Dad!

423
00:27:12,470 --> 00:27:13,200
You're here.

424
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:14,830
Sit.

425
00:27:31,990 --> 00:27:34,320
You sent a note saying you wanted to see me.

426
00:27:37,810 --> 00:27:39,010
It's been five years.

427
00:27:39,610 --> 00:27:40,790
It's time

428
00:27:41,260 --> 00:27:43,390
to settle the grudge between us today.

429
00:27:44,190 --> 00:27:46,720
I've been waiting for this day for a long time.

430
00:27:49,150 --> 00:27:51,110
Fate truly plays tricks on people.

431
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:53,190
Just a few days ago,

432
00:27:53,870 --> 00:27:56,230
I came to this very cell

433
00:27:56,670 --> 00:27:58,470
in this Zhong prison to see you.

434
00:27:59,590 --> 00:28:02,650
Who would have thought that now, the roles would be reversed,

435
00:28:02,650 --> 00:28:07,510
and I'd end up being the one condemned to death for treason and colluding with the enemy.

436
00:28:09,780 --> 00:28:10,580
You know what?

437
00:28:12,600 --> 00:28:14,330
The two words "being flexible"

438
00:28:15,300 --> 00:28:16,180
have led you to this end.

439
00:28:16,180 --> 00:28:17,500
I don't think so.

440
00:28:18,430 --> 00:28:20,230
If it weren't for Mr. Dai's plane

441
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:22,310
crashing on Daishan,

442
00:28:22,330 --> 00:28:24,440
I wouldn't be here.

443
00:28:26,470 --> 00:28:28,630
One can't defeat their fate.

444
00:28:29,310 --> 00:28:30,970
You really are incorrigible.

445
00:28:33,840 --> 00:28:35,390
A gun hidden in your hat?

446
00:28:35,510 --> 00:28:38,070
I taught you this trick

447
00:28:38,100 --> 00:28:39,120
back in the agent program.

448
00:28:39,120 --> 00:28:40,720
And now you use it against me.

449
00:28:40,910 --> 00:28:43,030
Do you know how much I want to kill you?

450
00:28:44,870 --> 00:28:46,200
I must avenge my father,

451
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,400
my sister, Fu Gui,

452
00:28:49,300 --> 00:28:50,940
and Mr. Huang.

453
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:53,210
You forgot someone.

454
00:28:56,860 --> 00:28:57,940
Xiao Ruotong.

455
00:28:59,330 --> 00:29:00,610
Go ahead, shoot me.

456
00:29:01,020 --> 00:29:02,460
Shoot me dead.

457
00:29:03,740 --> 00:29:05,260
I asked you here today

458
00:29:05,710 --> 00:29:08,310
because I want you to end me with your own hands.

459
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:10,070
I, Zhou Zhifei,

460
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:13,110
don't want to die

461
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:15,380
at the hands of some nobodies.

462
00:29:15,380 --> 00:29:17,340
Dying by your gun feels worth it.

463
00:29:17,360 --> 00:29:17,880
Come on.

464
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,740
I'm different from you.

465
00:29:34,780 --> 00:29:36,750
Instead of settling a personal grudge with a single shot,

466
00:29:36,750 --> 00:29:37,790
the people's bullets

467
00:29:37,790 --> 00:29:39,520
and the public trial of history

468
00:29:40,110 --> 00:29:43,170
have far greater significance in serving as a warning.

469
00:29:47,250 --> 00:29:48,490
As an agent,

470
00:29:49,910 --> 00:29:51,560
you have to be ruthless.

471
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:54,810
That's something you still haven't learned from me.

472
00:29:55,190 --> 00:29:57,120
I really want to ask you a question.

473
00:29:57,510 --> 00:30:00,640
I've been lying in this bed of yours for the past two days.

474
00:30:02,630 --> 00:30:04,390
At night, they turn off the lights.

475
00:30:04,390 --> 00:30:06,320
When the lights go out, I get scared

476
00:30:07,040 --> 00:30:09,550
and feel like I'm falling into a dark,

477
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,250
bottomless pit,

478
00:30:13,450 --> 00:30:14,980
falling deeper and deeper,

479
00:30:15,110 --> 00:30:16,960
never reaching the bottom.

480
00:30:21,470 --> 00:30:22,880
I'm so frightened.

481
00:30:25,490 --> 00:30:26,490
Gu Yizhong,

482
00:30:27,230 --> 00:30:29,040
how did you manage

483
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:32,590
to bear the name of a traitor for five years,

484
00:30:33,190 --> 00:30:34,790
being spat upon by thousands

485
00:30:35,910 --> 00:30:37,710
and with your family destroyed,

486
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:39,830
and still make it to today?

487
00:30:50,470 --> 00:30:52,070
Mr. Sicheng once said:

488
00:30:53,550 --> 00:30:55,150
"Arches above become beams,

489
00:30:55,630 --> 00:30:57,290
arches below become columns.

490
00:30:58,510 --> 00:31:00,310
Beams and columns are straight,

491
00:31:00,550 --> 00:31:01,810
but arches are curved.

492
00:31:03,110 --> 00:31:05,240
Curves and straight lines alternate,

493
00:31:06,630 --> 00:31:08,360
so the strength is boundless."

494
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:17,150
I see.

495
00:31:19,190 --> 00:31:21,390
You used curves against straight lines

496
00:31:22,350 --> 00:31:24,430
and outplayed my "being flexible."

497
00:31:25,150 --> 00:31:26,680
Zhou Zhifei, you are wrong.

498
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:27,790
It was faith.

499
00:31:29,450 --> 00:31:30,390
To live in this world,

500
00:31:30,390 --> 00:31:31,790
one must have some faith.

501
00:31:33,790 --> 00:31:35,520
But you have lost these things.

502
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:38,170
You're not worthy of being human.

503
00:31:44,430 --> 00:31:45,230
Zhou Zhifei,

504
00:31:45,750 --> 00:31:46,750
it's time.

505
00:31:47,390 --> 00:31:47,920
Let's go.

506
00:31:52,150 --> 00:31:53,950
Let me ask you one last question:

507
00:31:59,390 --> 00:32:00,870
Are you Lonely Boat?

508
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:53,230
[May Mr. Gu Xixing Rest in Peace]

509
00:33:54,350 --> 00:33:54,870
Dad,

510
00:33:56,830 --> 00:33:58,070
have you seen it?

511
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:02,540
The Japanese have been defeated.

512
00:34:02,790 --> 00:34:04,590
Our enemies have faced justice.

513
00:34:06,260 --> 00:34:07,660
The country is restored.

514
00:34:08,330 --> 00:34:09,370
The sky is clear.

515
00:34:10,790 --> 00:34:11,780
It's dawn.

516
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:15,310
Please rest in peace.

517
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:26,870
[The Tomb of the Patriotic Martyr, My Father, Mr. Gu Xixing]

518
00:34:27,060 --> 00:34:28,320
Where should we put it?

519
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,050
What about this one?

520
00:34:30,570 --> 00:34:31,850
How to fit it?

521
00:34:34,270 --> 00:34:34,870
Junsheng.

522
00:34:34,889 --> 00:34:36,150
Where should we put it?

523
00:34:36,219 --> 00:34:38,469
-What are you playing?
-Sir, you're here.

524
00:34:38,469 --> 00:34:39,190
Sir.

525
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:43,679
Uncle, Auntie has left.

526
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:56,360
Haimo!

527
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,120
Haimo.

528
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:08,030
My name is Lin Shujuan.

529
00:35:12,070 --> 00:35:13,070
Are you leaving,

530
00:35:14,430 --> 00:35:15,220
Shujuan?

531
00:35:20,660 --> 00:35:22,170
My cousin-in-law said

532
00:35:22,990 --> 00:35:25,850
that my brother died in an air battle over Changsha.

533
00:35:27,450 --> 00:35:28,840
I want to go there and see

534
00:35:29,850 --> 00:35:31,730
if I can find his tombstone,

535
00:35:35,470 --> 00:35:36,990
and then go to Chongqing

536
00:35:38,250 --> 00:35:40,010
to visit Mount Gele for him.

537
00:35:42,950 --> 00:35:43,590
I...

538
00:35:44,640 --> 00:35:46,050
I'll go with you.

539
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,830
No need, Mr. Gu.

540
00:35:52,520 --> 00:35:53,960
I know your heart

541
00:35:55,900 --> 00:35:57,820
always belongs to Xiao Ruotong.

542
00:35:59,870 --> 00:36:01,230
No one can replace her.

543
00:36:02,790 --> 00:36:03,690
I don't want someone

544
00:36:03,690 --> 00:36:05,550
whose heart doesn't belong to me.

545
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:09,920
Besides,

546
00:36:10,700 --> 00:36:13,160
we've been fake husband and wife for 5 years.

547
00:36:14,770 --> 00:36:16,170
I want to be myself again.

548
00:36:25,550 --> 00:36:26,410
What about you?

549
00:36:28,950 --> 00:36:30,270
What are your plans?

550
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:37,680
Well...

551
00:36:38,790 --> 00:36:41,850
Yizhong Architecture Research Society has reopened.

552
00:36:42,160 --> 00:36:44,220
I want to return to my old profession.

553
00:36:45,510 --> 00:36:47,110
Since the War of Resistance,

554
00:36:47,350 --> 00:36:50,270
many ancient buildings in Suzhou have been damaged.

555
00:36:50,270 --> 00:36:52,730
If there's no professional to restore them,

556
00:36:53,510 --> 00:36:55,750
they'll probably fall into ruin.

557
00:36:57,570 --> 00:37:00,170
This suits you better than working as an agent.

558
00:37:09,310 --> 00:37:12,870
Goodbye, Mr. Gu.

559
00:37:16,750 --> 00:37:17,630
Goodbye.

560
00:37:53,100 --> 00:37:56,120
[Three months later]

561
00:38:03,750 --> 00:38:04,750
Thank you.

562
00:38:16,200 --> 00:38:17,000
Are you busy?

563
00:38:19,230 --> 00:38:20,050
Yes.

564
00:38:20,990 --> 00:38:24,320
The Architecture Research Society has nothing to do today?

565
00:38:25,120 --> 00:38:26,580
In the current situation,

566
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:30,080
what business could the Architecture Research Society have?

567
00:38:30,080 --> 00:38:31,710
Why haven't the people from the Taihu Lake

568
00:38:31,710 --> 00:38:32,870
contacted you yet?

569
00:38:34,370 --> 00:38:36,100
They've all moved to Shandong.

570
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:39,450
You've been left behind again?

571
00:38:39,550 --> 00:38:40,340
No.

572
00:38:41,100 --> 00:38:42,200
Division Commander Luo said

573
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:43,720
he would send someone to contact me soon

574
00:38:43,720 --> 00:38:45,520
and take me to the Shandong base.

575
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:47,060
Junsheng.

576
00:38:47,590 --> 00:38:48,790
Junsheng, come here.

577
00:38:52,090 --> 00:38:52,880
Junsheng,

578
00:38:53,050 --> 00:38:54,510
why are your shoes on the wrong feet again?

579
00:38:54,510 --> 00:38:56,800
It was Uncle who put them on for me.

580
00:38:58,070 --> 00:39:00,110
Can you be more concerned about the child?

581
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:01,030
To me,

582
00:39:01,550 --> 00:39:04,950
raising a child is harder than restoring ancient buildings.

583
00:39:05,270 --> 00:39:07,470
I told you to keep Miss Haimo,

584
00:39:07,750 --> 00:39:08,670
but you didn't.

585
00:39:09,190 --> 00:39:10,790
Now you regret it, don't you?

586
00:39:11,110 --> 00:39:12,270
Do you miss her?

587
00:39:14,010 --> 00:39:15,070
Let me tell you,

588
00:39:15,730 --> 00:39:17,450
you won't find another girl like Haimo

589
00:39:17,450 --> 00:39:18,980
anywhere in the world.

590
00:39:19,190 --> 00:39:20,960
Her name is Lin Shujuan.

591
00:39:21,310 --> 00:39:22,380
I don't care what her name is.

592
00:39:22,380 --> 00:39:24,040
You shouldn't have let her go.

593
00:39:24,040 --> 00:39:25,550
You've lived together for five years.

594
00:39:25,550 --> 00:39:27,950
How can you have no feelings for each other?

595
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:29,790
You were afraid to express

596
00:39:29,790 --> 00:39:30,920
your true feelings.

597
00:39:30,940 --> 00:39:31,800
Hypocritical.

598
00:39:36,050 --> 00:39:39,080
