599
00:39:44,110 --> 00:39:49,940
♫As pretty as a flower♫

600
00:39:51,040 --> 00:39:53,230
♫Her brows are like willow leaves and her eyes have tender, lingering looks♫

601
00:39:53,290 --> 00:39:55,620
♫She has a delicate nose and a red cherry-like little mouth♫

602
00:39:55,620 --> 00:39:57,850
♫A big, big flower♫

603
00:39:57,870 --> 00:40:06,670
♫Tucked at her temple♫

604
00:40:10,810 --> 00:40:17,670
[Feng Garden Story-telling Theatre]

605
00:40:29,980 --> 00:40:44,710
♫The green waters ripple in the cool breeze♫

606
00:40:50,060 --> 00:41:02,460
♫Making the summer feel exceptionally long and refreshing♫

607
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:19,040
♫Summer is long, and the lotus are fragrant♫

608
00:41:44,110 --> 00:41:44,910
Sir,

609
00:41:46,350 --> 00:41:48,670
among the famous lines of poetry about Suzhou,

610
00:41:48,670 --> 00:41:50,670
I like the Song poet Yang Wanli's

611
00:41:51,660 --> 00:41:54,520
"Do not blame the lone boat for drifting aimlessly;

612
00:41:55,230 --> 00:41:58,270
my very self is but a wandering vessel."

613
00:42:06,450 --> 00:42:08,190
I prefer Du Fu's

614
00:42:09,790 --> 00:42:12,320
"I am a lonely boat yearning for my hometown."

615
00:42:20,390 --> 00:42:22,070
Hello, Comrade Lonely Boat.

616
00:42:37,290 --> 00:42:40,960
♫Wisps of clouds♫

617
00:42:41,490 --> 00:42:44,380
♫Adrift in the sky♫

618
00:42:45,750 --> 00:42:49,530
♫A gentle breeze whispers by♫

619
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:50,350
